  <brief_title>New Vectorcardiogram Analysis a Good Predictor of Coronary Disease in Patients With Normal Rest 12-leads ECG</brief_title>
  <official_title>Spacial Relation of QRS-T Vectocardiogram is a Good Predictor of Coronary Disease in Patients With Normal Rest 12-leads ECG</official_title>
  <sponsors>
